if (num % 2 == 0) {

printf("%d is even.", num);

} else {

printf("%d is odd.", num);

}

Test Again

If num = 4 : 4 % 2  is 0  → even (correct!).

If num = 5 : 5 % 2  is 1  → odd (correct!).

