c

if (a < b) {

return a;

} else {

return b;

}

🔹 Analogy:

"Pick the apple that weighs less."

Example 4: Odd/Even Check

Task: Return "Even" if a number is divisible by 2, else "Odd".

c

int num = 4;

printf("%s", (num % 2 == 0) ? "Even" : "Odd");

